name: Electrical Procrastination
description:
This game was made for the Low Effort Game jam 2. You are a electrician robot that procrastinated and now has to fix all these problems that have risen. If the generator is under stress for more than a minute then you'll have more problems. 

Controls - WASD to move, E to interact, SPACE to jump.

I put little to no effort in this so do not expect much.
